    <p>US distribution runs through Englewood Cliffs New Jersey. For LA service, parts lead times run 3-7 days on common service components, 5-10 days on specialty Italian-factory-specific parts — slightly longer than the Anaheim (Hestan) or Irvine (BSH brands) LA-proximity advantage, but reasonable for a European-origin brand routing through East Coast distribution.</p>
